response.overview: After getting into a serious car accident, a TV director discovers an underground sub-culture of scarred, omnisexual car-crash victims, and he begins to use car accidents and the raw sexual energy they produce to try to rejuvenate his sex life with his wife.
response.tagline: Shocking. Powerful. Scandalous. Provocative. Erotic. Brilliant.
